  - **Year 1:** {Detailed monthly projections}
  - **Year 2-3:** {Quarterly projections}
  - **Year 4-5:** {Annual projections}
- **Growth Assumptions:** {Key assumptions driving growth}
- **Scenario Analysis:** {Best case, worst case, most likely}

### Unit Economics
