## Operational Audit

### Process Audit
```yaml
operational_audit:
  process_evaluation:
    efficiency_assessment: {Process efficiency and productivity}
    effectiveness_assessment: {Process goal achievement}
    economy_assessment: {Resource utilization optimization}

